":100002601,"comment_content":"我本来一直纠结在重承诺和产品质量&#47;工程质量之间的矛盾。很多时候产品需要打磨，代码也需要打磨，然后我们又要按时交付。现在想来，我们宁愿要多估计点时间，把工程质量做好，尽量做到不break 承诺。然后在这个过程中定时做复盘，而且要到细节处去做复盘，逐步提高每一个团队成员的效率。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":260249,"user_name":"手太黑","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1930191,"ip_address":"","ucode":"02C2BDA886A64A","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1d/73/cf/4d204fbb.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1604970172,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1604970172","product_id":100002601,"comment_content":"从小事入手，不惧试错但是也需要控制错误，以承诺立信任。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":227669,"user_name":"悟空来 |  Arthur李华栋  |  👍","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1019969,"ip_address":"","ucode":"79F1A9DDF568C2","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/90/41/9113d93f.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1592450591,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1592450591","product_id":100002601,"comment_content":"没有权利的ceo这个理解高度非常高","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":227320,"user_name":"树叶","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1038619,"ip_address":"","ucode":"347261AED4A2B8","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/d9/1b/e4e04a41.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1592357657,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1592357657","product_id":100002601,"comment_content":"工作中经常遇到需求变更带来的信任度的降低要怎么办？即使PRD思考多 但毕竟是一人力，实现方式还是可能再发布前调整。🤣","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":87333,"user_name":"旺旺","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1213887,"ip_address":"","ucode":"161B267F67EBCA","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/85/bf/5c5e86bb.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555570633,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555570633","product_id":100002601,"comment_content":"产品经理对团队的影响力问题——信任。<br>逐步建立信任，完成一次+1分，未完成一次-10分。万一未完成，也不要一味